title: Zdravko Počivalšek
summary: Zdravko Počivalšek (born 25 November 1957) is a Slovenian politician. Since 13 March 2020, he has been Minister of Economic Development and Technology in the 14th Government of Slovenia. He also had this role in the 12th and 13th Government of Slovenia.
content:
Zdravko Počivalšek (born 25 November 1957) is a Slovenian politician. Since 13 March 2020, he has been Minister of Economic Development and Technology in the 14th Government of Slovenia. He also had this role in the 12th and 13th Government of Slovenia.
